    "question_id" : 22697,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>I started using mocks through JMock, but eventually transitioned to use EasyMock. EasyMock was just that, --easier-- and provided a syntax that felt more natural. I haven't switched since.</p>\n"
