      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Caveat: some things like mocking final methods are only possible in Powermock for EasyMock and not for Mockito. It&#39;s a bit of a gotcha when you don&#39;t use it that frequently. I was wondering why something wasn&#39;t working then I realised it&#39;s only listed under the Easymock section of the doco."
